snippet.title: Domiverse - How to play - Glomorf
snippet.description:
How to play Glomorf

Last winner of the spit contest in his planet, he is the champion they were waiting for!
Glomorf spit bouncing bullets and can walk on walls and ceilings.

http://domiverse.be

Steam store: http://store.steampowered.com/app/598880/Domiverse/
